      "updated": 1773472189793,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Feature Store Inputs:\n- team form (last N)\n- venue-adjusted strength\n- phase metrics (PP/Middle/Death)\n- toss & decision impact\n- wicket profile\n\nTraining:\n- baseline Logistic Regression\n- XGBoost/LightGBM/CatBoost\n- Optuna tuning\n- SHAP explainability\n- calibration (Platt/Isotonic)\n\nTracking:\n- MLflow experiments + model registry",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Feature Store Inputs:\n- team form (last N)\n- venue-adjusted strength\n- phase metrics (PP/Middle/Death)\n- toss & decision impact\n- wicket profile\n\nTraining:\n- baseline Logistic Regression\n- XGBoost/LightGBM/CatBoost\n- Optuna tuning\n- SHAP explainability\n- calibration (Platt/Isotonic)\n\nTracking:\n- MLflow experiments + model registry",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
