      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data Monitoring:\n- schema + range checks\n- freshness SLA\n- null/duplicate spikes\n\nModel Monitoring:\n- Log Loss, Brier, ROC-AUC\n- prediction drift (Evidently)\n- segment-wise performance\n\nAutomated Retraining:\n- daily trigger\n- N new matches / M deliveries\n- drift trigger\n- champion/challenger promotion gates",
