      "text": "- Orchestration: Prefect/Airflow     - Transformations: dbt     - Data Quality: Great Expectations\n- Storage: DuckDB (dev) + PostgreSQL/Cloud Warehouse (prod)\n- CI/CD: GitHub Actions (test, lint, build, deploy)     - Containers: Docker + docker-compose\n- Governance: data contracts, model versioning, rollback policy, audit logs",
